Scalatra is a tiny web framework for Scala, that follows the principles of the Sinatra Ruby web framework. It was originally known as Step and it is the framework behind the RESTful backend that is used by LinkedIn Signal.

git clone git://github.com/Srirangan/simple-scalatra-archetype.git simple-scalatra-archetype
cd simple-scalatra-archetype
mvn install


mvn archetype:generate -DarchetypeArtifactId=simple-scalatra-archetype -DarchetypeGroupId=org.scalatra -DarchetypeVersion=1.0-SNAPSHOT -DgroupId=de.coastal -DartifactId=helloworld
cd helloworld
mvn install
mvn jetty:run

localhost:8080/helloworld
